The paper focuses on machine learning and interpretability, which are core topics in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques (cs.CE) and probabilistic models (cs.AI) to improve the accuracy of interpretable models. Additionally, the paper uses decision trees (cs.DS) and linear models (cs.CR) as examples of interpretable models.
